{"tid":1085041,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[c++]有code唔識，求指教","createTime":"2019-03-31T00:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T01:05:52.000Z","uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd14c05c528b4bc67197702b883eee4ee568260","tid":1085041,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T00:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想問<br />\n<br />\n喺某a.h入面 <br />\n<blockquote>#define XXX</blockquote><br />\n又喺後來嘅某b.h入面<br />\n<blockquote>#include &quot;a.h&quot;<br />\n<br />\nint XXX f(int x){<br />\nreturn 1;<br />\n}</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地有咩關係？<br />\n係唔係比編譯器睇架咋？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\nc.h c.c<br />\n<blockquote>#include &quot;b.h&quot;<br />\n...<br />\nd=f(1);<br />\n...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係main.cpp就要加extern先用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>#include &quot;d.h&quot; <br />\n//並知道header入面同上面嘅header有關<br />\n//連同做好晒防重覆嘅ifdef define endif<br />\n<br />\nextern int XXX f(){int x}<br />\nint main(){<br />\nf();<br />\n}</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解要加extern先用到，平時include咗唔係就可以直接用架咩？<br />\n<br />\n係唔係因為 d.h有d32.dll 同d32.lib?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係巧辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e2d05fd1934e45ef25c81d1a7227cab1d48622","tid":1085041,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10422034/when-to-use-extern-in-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fquestions%2F10422034%2Fwhen-to-use-extern-in-c&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP98sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=f367f743\" target=\"_blank\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10422034/when-to-use-extern-in-c</a>"},{"pid":"5952ce93041f3bf2b7a83ddcf30bc5d524c6b40f","tid":1085041,"uid":147721,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"你可唔可以將你啲code寫多幾行 變成一個可以reproduce 既例子<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣 我而家咁啱明你問咩 但係你以後再有問題 未必會有人明"},{"pid":"7f1d3de048aaa6614545ce5ac4f8f39c5f228082","tid":1085041,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e2e2d05fd1934e45ef25c81d1a7227cab1d48622","tid":1085041,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10422034/when-to-use-extern-in-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fquestions%2F10422034%2Fwhen-to-use-extern-in-c&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP98sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=f367f743\" target=\"_blank\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10422034/when-to-use-extern-in-c</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"我都係唔明<br />\n佢係變數先要寫extern聲明<br />\n函數一向默認extern<br />\n<br />\n不過會唔會係因為有另一個extern &quot;C&quot;包住左header 入面嘅函數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變左局部<br />\n<br />\n所以加extern去揾返佢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12ecf746f4ad0138089f59925b7a94e7fa90be7","tid":1085041,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5952ce93041f3bf2b7a83ddcf30bc5d524c6b40f","tid":1085041,"uid":147721,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"你可唔可以將你啲code寫多幾行 變成一個可以reproduce 既例子<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣 我而家咁啱明你問咩 但係你以後再有問題 未必會有人明"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"我自己都唔明啊，我係調用緊人地嘅src<br />\n#cry#do 我可能需要成份upload<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0e41a6aa7203ba5c2b271b317f9d95688f2c61","tid":1085041,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f12ecf746f4ad0138089f59925b7a94e7fa90be7","tid":1085041,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5952ce93041f3bf2b7a83ddcf30bc5d524c6b40f","tid":1085041,"uid":147721,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"你可唔可以將你啲code寫多幾行 變成一個可以reproduce 既例子<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣 我而家咁啱明你問咩 但係你以後再有問題 未必會有人明"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"我自己都唔明啊，我係調用緊人地嘅src<br />\n#cry#do 我可能需要成份upload<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"你咪慢慢逐part縮"},{"pid":"0951be3e4367a4856d4b8c1af0095187c3b4e1b2","tid":1085041,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:05:52.000Z","msg":"關於 include file 同點解要 extern<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8zFOFtaysI?list=PLeGk08zVu454WgM_8uE-dUayT_EOoVEQS&amp;t=1602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8zFOFtaysI%3Flist%3DPLeGk08zVu454WgM_8uE-dUayT_EOoVEQS%26t%3D1602&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP98sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=2c470537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8zFOFtaysI?list=PLeGk08zVu454WgM_8uE-dUayT_EOoVEQS&amp;t=1602</a><br />\n<br />\n而 extern &quot;C&quot; 係因為 C++ 有 function overload 所以個 function name 會加埋個 type name, (e.g.  my_func@int, my_func@double)<br />\n咁樣會令 C++ 同 C (not C++) function linking 時唔夾, 所以 extern &quot;C&quot; 係話俾 compiler 知, 依個 function 用 &quot;C&quot; 既明命名方法 (即係無左 function 名後面既 type suffix)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0eGag50SFc0?list=PLeGk08zVu4566pxRefXH0zr1FDL4BGUUG&amp;t=510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0eGag50SFc0%3Flist%3DPLeGk08zVu4566pxRefXH0zr1FDL4BGUUG%26t%3D510&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP98sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=b83343d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0eGag50SFc0?list=PLeGk08zVu4566pxRefXH0zr1FDL4BGUUG&amp;t=510</a>"}]}